Rating: 3
I made this recipe when it was first published. Instant addiction!I have made it many dozen times since. I often enjoy it as an entire light meal with just good bread or crackers. According to mood I have used more lemon, capers, or feta cheese and almost always use much less oil (although good olive oil certainly enhances taste). I don't have a mandoline but enjoy the crunch of very thinly sliced fennel. A winner in my book!

