Rating: 4
This was surprisingly good. My husband is not a big fan of fennel, and he absolutely loved it! It did not taste strongly of anise nor were the tomatoes I used especially ripe, but the lemon juice really brightened up the flavor. It's crunchy and just a great combination of flavors. And it's low fat! It would be good all year round.

