Rating: 3
Very happy to tell you that this is delicious. I cut the recipe in half (1 fennel bulb and two tomatoes) for two and felt there was still enough for four people. You'll want to adjust the other ingredients to your taste. I liked more of everything. It was excellent with salmon. You just need a very sharp knife for the fennel and I like a little thicker slice than stated "paper-thin." Quarter your tomatoes length wise also and slice about 1/4" thick. A lovely slaw. Stays fresh overnight.